    "Evening shows the highest number of thefts, with more than 32,000 reported cases.\n",
    "\n",
    "Afternoon comes next, slightly above 20,000 cases.\n",
    "\n",
    "Morning follows closely, also near 19,000 cases.\n",
    "\n",
    "Night is the period with the lowest theft rate, with around 17,000 thefts.\n",
    "\n",
    "This trend suggests that vehicle theft is primarily an evening activity, potentially linked to reduced visibility, higher street activity, or cars being parked for longer durations without supervision."
